-- Semadil<br>
<br>
It's been pointed out numerous times that &quot;under God&quot; was amended to the Pledge of Allegiance during the Cold War for whatever religious and political reasons of the day. Despite this, and as cynical as I can be, it doesn't bother me overmuch. That being said...<br>
<br>
Respecting the views of the people who gave us liberties? Well, are you saying that we should keep the pledge as it is for old time's sake (that would be as far back as the 1950's when people from various walks of life were investigated before a panel thanks to a senator with a list of names of possible communists) although it blatantly goes against the Constitution then as it does now? That the change to the pledge was made with good intentions does nothing to erase its unconstitutionality. What if someone wants to get away with another Constitutional inconsistency? Who endows us, anyone, to pardon a religious slip but stick to the letter in other areas?<br>
<br>
Respect has nothing to do with aspiring or conceding to a view that goes contrary to the principles laid down before McCarthy hysteria took up. BTW, &quot;In God We Trust&quot; wasn't made an official standard on mint until 1956. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=366.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=366.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=366.topic&start=61&stop=70>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=366.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=366.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=366.topic&index=20><img src=http://quellious-collective.com/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=366.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.threadControl?topicID=366.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=366.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13